      "text": [
        "1141 - وَ رَوَى اَلْحَلَبِيُّ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ أَنَّهُ قَالَ: «لاَ أَرَى بِالصُّفُوفِ بَيْنَ اَلْأَسَاطِينِ بَأْساً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1141 - Al-Halabi narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) that He said:\n\"I see no harm in rows (of prayer) being between the columns (pillars).\""
        ]
      }
    }
